I think we need to bring back the dreaded Network Police, and
enforce maintenance of domains.  If sites are to be anti-social,
then maybe they should be disconnected.  It is a bit extreme,
but...  what other recourse is there?

-Philip

P.S.	Given the NICs flakiness lately, perhaps we should move
	this list to another machine?

